2026-03-21 12:01:13,733 [INFO] ai_scientist.tools.semantic_scholar: Response Content: {"total": 78, "offset": 0, "next": 10, "data": [{"paperId": "bfed3d4c959b64148811376965db84f77ea8292e", "title": "Transforming Science with Large Language Models: A Survey on AI-assisted Scientific Discovery, Experimentation, Content Generation, and Evaluation", "venue": "arXiv.org", "year": 2025, "citationCount": 35, "openAccessPdf": {"url": "", "status": null, "license": null, "disclaimer": "Notice: Paper or abstract available at https://arxiv.org/abs/2502.05151, which is subject to the licens
