2026-03-21 12:12:52,168 [INFO] ai_scientist.tools.semantic_scholar: Response Content: {"total": 54, "offset": 0, "next": 10, "data": [{"paperId": "a660f45d2c225294d11ceb89102f86a156dc5d54", "title": "CritiCal: Can Critique Help LLM Uncertainty or Confidence Calibration?", "venue": "arXiv.org", "year": 2025, "citationCount": 3, "openAccessPdf": {"url": "", "status": null, "license": null, "disclaimer": "Notice: Paper or abstract available at https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.24505, which is subject to the license by the author or copyright owner provided with this content. Please go to t
