2026-03-21 12:14:05,776 [INFO] ai_scientist.tools.semantic_scholar: Response Content: {"total": 14, "offset": 0, "next": 10, "data": [{"paperId": "2e265a76dafaef27bf3a1b8c2279b06cb2d8be6a", "title": "Artificial intelligence streamlines diagnosis and assessment of prognosis in Brugada syndrome: a systematic review and meta-analysis", "venue": "Connected Health And Telemedicine", "year": 2024, "citationCount": 2, "openAccessPdf": {"url": "https://f.oaes.cc/xmlpdf/ee70f598-40e2-4bc9-b448-e4711a6bd903/chatmed4003.pdf", "status": "GOLD", "license": "CCBY", "disclaimer": "Notice: Paper
