2026-03-21 12:17:45,561 [INFO] ai_scientist.tools.semantic_scholar: Response Content: {"total": 3, "offset": 0, "data": [{"paperId": "030daf1a91297f1f3b6dcd0b7f2a06a991414dee", "title": "A Comparison of AI-Assisted and Manually Scored Student Projects in\n Physiology Education", "venue": "Physiology", "year": 2025, "citationCount": 0, "openAccessPdf": {"url": "", "status": null, "license": null, "disclaimer": "Notice: Paper or abstract available at https://api.unpaywall.org/v2/10.1152/physiol.2025.40.s1.0456?email=<INSERT_YOUR_EMAIL> or https://doi.org/10.1152/physiol.2025.40.s1.
